@@TJvStaticText.Create
Summary
  Creates and initializes a new TJvStaticText object.
Description
  Use Create to create and initialize a new TJvStaticText object.
  
  Create calls the inherited Create method, then sets the initial values for the control as follows: 

  * HintColor is set to clInfoBk.
  * csAcceptsControls is added to ControlStyle.  
Parameters
  AOwner - A component, typically the form, that is responsible for freeing the control.
See Also
  Destroy
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvStaticText.Destroy
Summary
  Destroys an instance of TJvStaticText.
Description
  Do not call Destroy directly in an application. Instead, call Free. Free verifies that the 
  TJvStaticText object is not nil and only then calls Destroy.
Parameters
  None.
See Also
  Create
